quarks.runtime.etiao

Class SettableForwarder<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • quarks.runtime.etiao.SettableForwarder<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of data on the stream.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, Consumer<T>

    public final class SettableForwarder<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Consumer<T>
    A forwarding Streamer whose destination can be changed. External synchronization or happens-before guarantees must be provided by the object owning an instance of SettableForwarder.
